Feeling so many things today…and when I find I’m overwhelmed by the world and how we choose to live in it…I instead try to focus on one small supportive action step I can take. ⁠
⁠
Here are orgs I’m giving to and following to help support our fellow humans in Ukraine. 💛💙🇺🇦⁠
⁠
Give what you can. Continue to amplify.⁠
And most of all, take good care of yourself. ❤️🙏🏽⁠
