PINKFISHES STANDS WITH UKRAINE 🇺🇦 

We were asked to join the ‘Beauty Brands Unite & Donate’ campaign, whereby we donated 20% of all sales from Saturday to a charity of our choice supporting Ukraine. 

We have chosen to support Save the Children - The Ukraine Appeal. 
They are planning to deliver lifesaving aid to 3.5 million vulnerable children and their families by:
💛Working in neighbouring countries to help the hundreds of thousands of people who have been forced to flee their homes.
💙Distributing essential supplies and winter kits of clothing and blankets as temperatures plunge below freezing.
💛Providing cash and vouchers to families to meet basic needs like food, rent and medicines.
💙Offering vital mental health and psychosocial support to children and their families.
💛Providing access to safe, inclusive, quality education.

For more information on how they are helping and to donate visit their website here: https://www.savethechildren.org.uk/how-you-can-help/emergencies/ukraine-appeal 

